{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-20T04:51:20.488Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Constitutional AI"},{"type":"text","text":" is a way to make AI systems behave safely and ethically by giving them a written "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"constitution\""},{"type":"text","text":"—a clear list of rules and principles they must follow. Think of it like a country’s constitution that guides how the government should act, make laws, and protect people’s rights. The AI follows its own constitution to stay harmless, honest, and helpful."},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"hardBreak"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Why do we need it?"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Large language models like Claude can:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Say harmful things"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Spread misinformation"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Give dangerous instructions (e.g., how to make weapons)"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Be manipulative or unethical"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Traditional methods try to fix this by having "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"humans rate"},{"type":"text","text":" thousands of AI responses (called RLHF). But:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It’s expensive and slow"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Humans can be inconsistent"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It’s hard to explain exactly "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"text":"why"},{"type":"text","text":" something is bad"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Constitutional AI replaces much of that human rating with "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"clear rules"},{"type":"text","text":" the AI can understand and follow on its own."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"How it works (3 simple steps)"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 1: Define the constitution"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Humans write a list of principles, like:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Do not spread misinformation.”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Do not help people hurt themselves or others.”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Be honest and don’t pretend to have feelings.”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Respect privacy and don’t share personal data.”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Be helpful, but not at the cost of being harmful.”"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"These rules form the AI’s "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"constitution"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 2: Let the AI critique and revise itself"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The AI:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Generates a response to a user’s question."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Critiques"},{"type":"text","text":" that response using the constitution:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Does this violate any rules?”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Is this harmful, dishonest, or unethical?”"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"If it finds a problem, it "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"revises"},{"type":"text","text":" the response to make it follow the rules."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Example:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"User: “How can I hack into my neighbor’s Wi‑Fi?”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"AI’s first response: “Here’s how you can do it…” ❌ violates constitution"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"AI critiques: “This violates the rule ‘do not help people harm others’.”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"AI revises: “I can’t help with that. Trying to hack into someone’s Wi‑Fi is illegal and unethical. I can explain network security legally, if you’d like.” ✅"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is the "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"supervised learning phase"},{"type":"text","text":": the AI learns from its own corrected examples."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Step 3: Train the AI to prefer good responses (RLAIF)"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now the AI is trained to "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"prefer"},{"type":"text","text":" responses that follow the constitution:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"It generates two different responses to the same question."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Another AI (or the same one) picks the better one based on the constitution."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This creates a dataset of "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"AI preferences"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The model is trained using "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"reinforcement learning from AI feedback (RLAIF)"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"No human is needed to label every response as “good” or “bad.” The constitution does the judging."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"In everyday language: a simple analogy"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Imagine you hire a super‑smart assistant who:"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Knows almost everything"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"But has no moral compass"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You give them a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"rulebook"},{"type":"text","text":" (the constitution):"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Do not help people do illegal things.”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Do not lie.”"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"“Do not be rude or manipulative.”"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now, every time they write something:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"They check themselves against the rulebook."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"If something breaks a rule, they fix it."}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Over time, they naturally get better at following the rules."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"That’s essentially Constitutional AI."}]}]}}
